casebody.head_matter:
In Re GRAND JURY SUBPOENA.
No. 18-948.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 19, 2019.
Motion of Reporters Committee for Freedom of the Press to intervene denied. Motion of respondent for leave to file redacted copies of the application for stay, response, and reply granted.
